OL,3,CCircus offers acrobatic displays with
OL,4,Ca twist
OL,6,FITV Meridian's Tom Savvides went
OL,7,Fbehind the scenes to meet the acts.
OL,9,FA circus with a difference has arrived
OL,10,Fon the South Coast. The company, Nofit
OL,11,FState, combines acrobatic displays
OL,12,Fwith emotional theatre.
OL,14,FThere are the acrobatic displays you'd
OL,15,Fexpect from a traditional circus, but
OL,16,Fthere's a twist to these performances,
OL,17,Fas they challenge prejudice and stand
OL,18,Fup for people from all walks of life.
