OL,6,FCalled Sabotage, this show portrays
OL,7,Fthe grittier and sometimes darker side
OL,8,Fof society but emphasises that
OL,9,Feveryone has a part to play.
OL,11,F"Sabotage is really about the
OL,12,Fsaboteurs and who they are. And they
OL,13,Fare the kind of the marginalised, the
OL,14,Fdisenfranchised, the outsiders and the
OL,15,Foutcasts," said artistic director, Tom
OL,16,FRack.
