OL,6,F"And they come together to create
OL,7,Fsomething beautiful and to support
OL,8,Fthemselves, to support each other, to
OL,9,Fstand up for themselves, to be heard,
OL,10,Fto be listened to, to be counted."
OL,12,FThe company NoFit State is currently
OL,13,Fon tour, stopping off in Brighton for
OL,14,Fa month.
OL,16,FA whole cast of performers are in full
OL,17,Fswing in a variety of emotional
OL,18,Fperformances.
