OL,6,FBesmir Sula spent many years in a
OL,7,Fwheelchair. He's now one of the acts
OL,8,Ftaking centre stage.
OL,10,F"Now I am here to live my dream. It's
OL,11,Fmy dream because I like to show the
OL,12,Fpeople why they doing what is my
OL,13,Fstory."
OL,15,FCreative director , Firenza Guidi said
OL,16,Fthe show takes months to prepare but
OL,17,Fwhen it all comes together, the
OL,18,Faudience leaves with some striking and
OL,19,Fpoignant memories and a drive to
OL,20,Fachieve.
